In this video, Naeem Bukhari discusses about the Fear of Tomorrow "AANE WALY KAL KA KHAUF" and beautifully advice the viewers to forget this fear and move forward with the same pace.

He states that do not spoil your future, stay in your present and forget about the past. This will conclude in a great success in your life. He advice not to fear about the day coming after.
